Deployment URL: [To be updated after cloud deployment]

Alternative deployment URLs (examples):
- https://car-dealership-portal.onrender.com
- https://car-dealership.azurewebsites.net
- https://car-dealership-portal-production.up.railway.app

Note: The actual deployment URL will depend on the cloud platform chosen for deployment.
For this capstone project, the application can be deployed to:
- Heroku (https://www.heroku.com)
- Render (https://render.com)
- Railway (https://railway.app)
- Azure Web Apps (https://azure.microsoft.com)
- AWS Elastic Beanstalk (https://aws.amazon.com)
- Google Cloud Run (https://cloud.google.com)

The application is configured for deployment with:
- Gunicorn as the WSGI server
- Static files collection
- Database migrations
- Environment variable configuration
- CORS settings for frontend-backend communication
